@startuml
!include ../../_common/style.puml
title watchdog 自动续期生命周期状态图

[*] --> DECISION
DECISION --> DISABLED : autoRenew=false
DECISION --> RUNNING : autoRenew=true

DISABLED : 不启动 watchdog
DISABLED --> [*]

RUNNING : 定时任务运行中
RUNNING : 每隔 renewInterval 调用 handle.renew()
RUNNING --> RUNNING : RENEWED\n续期成功
RUNNING --> LOST_NOT_FOUND : renew NOT_FOUND
RUNNING --> LOST_NOT_OWNER : renew NOT_OWNER
RUNNING --> PROVIDER_ERROR : renew PROVIDER_ERROR
RUNNING --> MAX_RENEW_EXCEEDED : reached maxRenewTime
RUNNING --> STOPPED : callback finished\nor handle released

LOST_NOT_FOUND : markLostOnce
LOST_NOT_FOUND : status=LOCK_LOST
LOST_NOT_FOUND : stage=RENEW
LOST_NOT_OWNER : markLostOnce
LOST_NOT_OWNER : status=LOCK_LOST
LOST_NOT_OWNER : stage=RENEW
PROVIDER_ERROR : publish PROVIDER_ERROR
PROVIDER_ERROR : stage=RENEW
PROVIDER_ERROR : 不确定是否失锁
MAX_RENEW_EXCEEDED : markLostOnce
MAX_RENEW_EXCEEDED : 停止续期
MAX_RENEW_EXCEEDED : 防止无限续期

LOST_NOT_FOUND --> STOPPED
LOST_NOT_OWNER --> STOPPED
PROVIDER_ERROR --> RUNNING : 策略允许继续尝试
PROVIDER_ERROR --> STOPPED : 策略选择停止
MAX_RENEW_EXCEEDED --> STOPPED
STOPPED --> [*]

note right of RUNNING
  watchdog 是 Java 内部定时续期任务。
  Redis 是底层锁存储。
end note

@enduml
